cate lattice work, keeping the furniture from appearing clunky. The set of drawers has an upholstered seat making it a convenient spot to put on or take off your shoes. Care has been taken to not block the natural light streaming in from the window.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"820\" height=\"820\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235421\/foyer-design-main-entrance-door.jpg\" alt=\"Entrance foyer design with seating, table and storage space makes a home entrance beautiful.\" class=\"wp-image-3989\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235421\/foyer-design-main-entrance-door.jpg 820w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235421\/foyer-design-main-entrance-door-150x150.jpg 150w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235421\/foyer-design-main-entrance-door-300x300.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235421\/foyer-design-main-entrance-door-768x768.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235421\/foyer-design-main-entrance-door-415x415.jpg 415w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235421\/foyer-design-main-entrance-door-417x416.jpg 417w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235421\/foyer-design-main-entrance-door-225x225.jpg 225w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235421\/foyer-design-main-entrance-door-475x475.jpg 475w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235421\/foyer-design-main-entrance-door-70x70.jpg 70w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 820px) 100vw, 820px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Build storage or seating or both in the area behind the main entrance door to utilise foyer space well<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img decoding=