-cupboards-ceiling.jpg\" alt=\"Entrance foyer area design with cupboard, wallpaper, decor, entryway furniture with storage and seating.\" class=\"wp-image-3991\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235432\/foyer-area-design-with-cupboards-ceiling.jpg 820w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235432\/foyer-area-design-with-cupboards-ceiling-150x150.jpg 150w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235432\/foyer-area-design-with-cupboards-ceiling-300x300.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235432\/foyer-area-design-with-cupboards-ceiling-768x768.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235432\/foyer-area-design-with-cupboards-ceiling-415x415.jpg 415w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235432\/foyer-area-design-with-cupboards-ceiling-417x416.jpg 417w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235432\/foyer-area-design-with-cupboards-ceiling-225x225.jpg 225w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235432\/foyer-area-design-with-cupboards-ceiling-475x475.jpg 475w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235432\/foyer-area-design-with-cupboards-ceiling-70x70.jpg 70w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 820px) 100vw, 820px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Build-in additional storage by vertically extending cupboards<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Complete end to end home interiors on a budget\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/12175818\/complete-end-to-end-home-interiors-on-a-budget.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Or Stay Low<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>After reaching for the skies, here\u2019s a foyer area design that achieves dramatic results by keeping it low. The wall area is clad in wood with an extra-long bench lining it. The bench has in built-in storage beneath in. Some box shelves and a few cushions further create space, comfort and style. The overall look is pristine and classy.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"820\" height=\"820\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235436\/foyer-area-design-with-low-seating-built-in-storage.jpg\" alt=\"House entrance lobby design with foyer seating, bench, wallpaper, storage area, shoe shelf and more.\" class=\"wp-image-3992\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235436\/foyer-area-design-with-low-seating-built-in-storage.jpg 820w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235436\/foyer-area-design-with-low-seating-built-in-storage-150x150.jpg 150w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235436\/foyer-area-design-with-low-seating-built-in-storage-300x300.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235436\/foyer-area-design-with-low-seating-built-in-storage-768x768.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235436\/foyer-area-design-with-low-seating-built-in-storage-415x415.jpg 415w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235436\/foyer-area-design-with-low-seating-built-in-storage-417x416.jpg 417w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235436\/foyer-area-design-with-low-seating-built-in-storage-225x225.jpg 225w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235436\/foyer-area-design-with-low-seating-built-in-storage-475x475.jpg 475w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235436\/foyer-area-design-with-low-seating-built-in-storage-70x70.jpg 70w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 820px) 100vw, 820px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Aim for graceful elegance with low seating with built-in storage<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Make A Grand Home Entrance Design<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Those wanting to make a big and bold impression, have your home entrance design play its part. Guests walking into this home will be greeted by graceful white columns set off against Prussian blue walls. A magnificent pedestal table acts as a lovely centrepiece and does justice to the size of the foyer. A richly intricate carpet atop hardwood floors completes the look of grandeur.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"820\" height=\"820\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235442\/home-entrance-design-pedestal-table-graceful-columns.jpg\" alt=\"Entrance decoration using table, modern entrance arch design, foyer wallpaper, wall decor, door design.\" class=\"wp-image-3993\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235442\/home-entrance-design-pedestal-table-graceful-columns.jpg 820w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235442\/home-entrance-design-pedestal-table-graceful-columns-150x150.jpg 150w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235442\/home-entrance-design-pedestal-table-graceful-columns-300x300.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235442\/home-entrance-design-pedestal-table-graceful-columns-768x768.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235442\/home-entrance-design-pedestal-table-graceful-columns-415x415.jpg 415w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235442\/home-entrance-design-pedestal-table-graceful-columns-417x416.jpg 417w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235442\/home-entrance-design-pedestal-table-graceful-columns-225x225.jpg 225w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\